Alstom Fires 445 Workers From Swiss Unit, 180 Resign, AWP Says

-- B y   C a r o l y n   B a n d e l
-- 
2011-03-17T17:41:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/alstom-fires-445-workers-from-swiss-unit-180-resign-awp-says.html
  Alstom SA (ALO)  will fire 445 workers
from its Swiss unit in the canton of Aargau, fewer than
expected, according to AWP, citing the company.  Alstom said 180 workers had resigned on their own, the
Swiss newswire reported today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carolyn Bandel in Zurich at 
 cbandel@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net . 